OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FA legal challenge has been filed
OL,7,Fagainst Gatwick Airport's #2.2 billion
OL,8,Fplans to add a second operating runway.
OL,10,FPlans for the expansion involve the
OL,11,Frepurposing of the current back-up
OL,12,Frunway at Gatwick Airport, allowing it
OL,13,Fto operate alongside the main runway.
OL,15,FAfter being approved by Transport
OL,16,FSecretary Heidi Alexander in
OL,17,FSeptember, it will enable an
OL,18,Fadditional 100,000 flights per year by
OL,19,Fthe late 2030s.
