OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FCampaign group, Communities against
OL,7,FGatwick Noise Emissions (CAGNE) says
OL,8,Fthe impact of the expansion on climate
OL,9,Fchange has not been properly assessed,
OL,10,Fand as a result development consent
OL,11,Fshould not have been granted.
OL,13,FCAGNE argues there are a number of
OL,14,Fgaps in the environmental assessment
OL,15,Fof the development.
