OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FThese include a failure to properly
OL,7,Fevaluate the significance of inbound
OL,8,Fflight emissions and a failure to
OL,9,Fassess the effect of non-carbon
OL,10,Fdioxide emissions on the climate. It
OL,11,Falso claims there was a failure to
OL,12,Faddress concerns over noise.
OL,14,FIt comes after Transport Secretary
OL,15,FHeidi Alexander was put on legal
OL,16,Fnotice by the group in October
OL,17,Ffollowing the decision to grant
OL,18,Fdevelopment consent for the expansion.
