OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FSally Pavey, chair of CAGNE said: "The
OL,7,Fonly guarantees Gatwick offered were
OL,8,Fsignificant increases in noise and
OL,9,Fmore pressure on our sewage system,
OL,10,Fwhilst increasing global warming to
OL,11,Fallow a huge increase in seasonal
OL,12,Fleisure flights exporting sterling out
OL,13,Fof the UK purse.
OL,15,F"It is absolutely shameful that
OL,16,Fresidents are forced to take legal
OL,17,Faction to hold a government to account.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
