OL,6,F"To build a brighter future, you must
OL,7,Flook to what is sustainable, to what
OL,8,Flegacy we wish to leave future
OL,9,Fgenerations.
OL,11,F"One that increases global warming per
OL,12,FGatwick flight, that costs less than a
OL,13,Ftrain fare to London, or one that
OL,14,Fpresents a sustainable future for all."
