OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FLeigh Day solicitor Julia Eriksen, who
OL,7,Frepresents CAGNE, said: "The impact of
OL,8,Fa second runway at Gatwick Airport
OL,9,Fwill undoubtedly be significant, and a
OL,10,Fthorough evaluation of the effects of
OL,11,Fthis on the environment should be a
OL,12,Fkey part of any proposal.
OL,14,F"However, our client says that the
OL,15,Fenvironmental impact has not been
OL,16,Fproperly assessed, and that
OL,17,Fdevelopment consent has been granted
OL,18,Fdespite a number of flaws in the
OL,19,Fplanning application."
