OL,3,CLegal challenge filed against second
OL,4,Crunway at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FA London Gatwick spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are aware that a claim for
OL,8,Fjudicial review has been lodged in the
OL,9,FHigh Court against the decision of the
OL,10,FSecretary of State for Transport to
OL,11,Fapprove our Northern Runway Project.
OL,13,F"We intend to participate in the
OL,14,Fproceedings as an Interested Party.
OL,15,FHowever, while legal proceedings are
OL,16,Fin progress it would not be
OL,17,Fappropriate to comment any further."
